    "Lara-Colón and Romo-Rodríguez [36], in their comparative study on the use of ChatGPT among Information Technology students at the University of Guayaquil, highlight how this virtual assistant enhances personalized learning experiences.",
    "Although its effectiveness and acceptance require further study, ChatGPT represents an innovative tool with the potential to transform higher education.Additionally, Ciprés et al. [37] discusses the impact of AI generative language models in higher education, addressing the challenges and opportunities they present.",
    "Models like ChatGPT support various educational areas but also pose ethical and practical challenges, such as academic integrity and data privacy.",
    "Ensuring responsible and equitable use of these technologies in the educational environment is essential.According to the research developed by Atlas [38], access to ChatGPT represents a significant advancement in managing diverse and complex tasks, offering substantial educational potential.",
    "A study integrating ChatGPT into Computer Engineering courses shows that most students (92.50%) find it useful and easy to use for academic tasks, though faculty support is lower (80%)."
